      • next

        public CommodityProfile.Builder next()
        Uses the values as set by the duration(Measurable), electricity(Measurable), gas(Measurable) and heat(Measurable) methods to create a new element. This does not reset the values, so if you call this method again it will create a second element that is equal to the first.
        Returns:
        This builder
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when the duration has not been set using duration(Measurable)
